---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Football Data Tools" description="Free football tools: build a fantasy planning squad, compare completed seasons, recalculate league tables and explore club finishing positions." canonical="/tools/">
  <div class="container prose">
    <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><span class="current">Tools</span></nav>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <h1>Football data tools</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Ask useful questions of the reviewed part of the Last Season archive.</p>
    </section>
    <div class="tool-grid section">
      <a class="tool-card" href="/fantasy-football/"><h2>Fantasy football helpers</h2><p>Plan a squad, compare opening fixtures, rank captains and find a team name.</p><span>Open fantasy lab →</span></a>
      <a class="tool-card" href="/tools/season-compare/"><h2>Compare seasons</h2><p>Compare champions, points, goals, club counts and leading scorers.</p><span>Open comparison →</span></a>
      <a class="tool-card" href="/tools/table-calculator/"><h2>Table calculator</h2><p>Recalculate a final table with alternative points for a win and draw.</p><span>Open calculator →</span></a>
      <a class="tool-card" href="/tools/club-history/"><h2>Club history explorer</h2><p>Plot a club's finishing positions across published, reviewed seasons.</p><span>Explore clubs →</span></a>
      <a class="tool-card" href="/search/"><h2>Archive search</h2><p>Find leagues, seasons, clubs, players, records and tools quickly.</p><span>Search the archive →</span></a>
    </div>
    <p class="callout">These tools use only seasons that pass the archive's consistency gate. <a href="/methodology/">Read the methodology</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
